Detailed Description

Basic implementation for a single model observer.

Derrived implementations can reimplement simplified OnUpdate method to be notified about model changes.

virtual bool imod::CSingleModelObserverBase::OnAttached ( imod::IModel *  modelPtr  )  [virtual]

This call back function will be called, if an observable object is about to be attached.

This function returns a true, if observable object is accepted by the implementation logic of the observer, otherwise the function returns a false.
